Supported you... of course.

198
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:26,000
Ê bergî Hemîd bî... ê niştî xawkê min.
 
The first one was Hamid... my nephew.

199
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:32,000
Wî pirr bi mera weke gotî, "Ella çêkin, çêkin," weleh eynî
