224
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:15,000
Yanî hebûnekî te, kesayetî te li ser kemîre, pirr xurt e.
 
I mean your presence, your personality on camera, is very
strong.

225
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:16,000
Sipas ji te ra.
 
Thank you.

226
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:18,000
